name: LongActingBetaAgonistsLABAAllergyIntolerance
title: Long Acting Beta Agonists (LABA) Allergy Intolerance
purpose: (Clinical Focus: SNOMED CT codes and RxNORM codes that could be returned by the FHIR Allergy Intolerance resource, and would indicate allergy or intolerance to LABA medications),(Data Element Scope: ALLERGY_INTOLERANCE:LABA),(Inclusion Criteria: RxNORM codes for individual medications that are LABA medications, and various SNOMED CT codes that would indicate allergy or intolerance to LABA medications as a class, or individual LABA medications),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
